    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and a generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and toss together – this is your <strong>balsamic salad</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 175ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[230ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with your <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and<strong> soft cheese </strong>– this is your<strong> creamy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
