    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>creamy stock</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Increase the heat to high and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened and the sausage meat is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>sausage, thyme & mushroom white ragù</strong></p>",
