      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sausage, thyme & mushroom white ragù with spaghetti </strong>with the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese </strong>sprinkled over the top</p><p>Serve the <strong>balsamic salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
